    "created_at": "2014-04-15T13:37:51Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-04-15T13:37:51Z",
    "body": "The original blocker for this was that closures didn't borrow their contents, so an implementation was unsound. The source of this unsoundness has been fixed, and this was attempted in #11905. The PR was abandoned because the borrowing became too unmanageable (prevented too many legitimate situations).\n\nA new effort may uncover something different, and this may need to be a language feature rather than a library if we do indeed add it.\n",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
